{"tid":1599040,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【科學討論】好多狗都戴紅色護目鏡，係咪擋到藍或綠laser?","createTime":"2019-09-27T18:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:00:21.000Z","uid":90735,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f298795252ad5024c64161bc830e1d05ba801b","tid":1599040,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"Mon post狗唔好亂諗嘢，「好多狗都戴紅色護目鏡」意思係下面呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.lazyliving.co.nz/image/cache/catalog/incoming/images/full/d/f/dff80907-c294-c847-1023-57e321250690-10049-800x800.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lazyliving.co.nz%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fcatalog%2Fincoming%2Fimages%2Ffull%2Fd%2Ff%2Fdff80907-c294-c847-1023-57e321250690-10049-800x800.jpeg&h=1c433294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">小弟養狗，見好多街坊都玩laser，我驚laser整親我隻狗，所以想買適合護目鏡俾家犬</span><br />\n<br />\n睇下呢條測試片，紅色護目鏡擋到<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></strong>及<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>綠</strong></span>光，反而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></strong>光擋唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/upCsVrKrW7M?t=91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FupCsVrKrW7M%3Ft%3D91&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=798b2716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/upCsVrKrW7M?t=91</a><br />\n<br />\n藍色好似激光劍咁癲，雖然紅色laser 相對冇咁過癮，但係咪代表相對較難trace 源頭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QXgg2MQj03I?t=480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQXgg2MQj03I%3Ft%3D480&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=5d9bb30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QXgg2MQj03I?t=480</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MfyL7IZl4_I?t=39\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMfyL7IZl4_I%3Ft%3D39&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=2bd054ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MfyL7IZl4_I?t=39</a><br />\n<br 